    <detaileddescription>
<para>Methods and definitions necessary to fetch information about the underlying data sources. Dataproviders are the underlying mechanism for collecting the requested metadata and are abstracted away by the API. The following definitions can be used to get more information (e.g., to report detailed version information). </para>
